Image::Xpm
==========

Image::Xpm is a Perl module for loading, creating, manipulating and
saving xpm image files.

INSTALLATION
------------

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

Or with modern CPAN.pm ($CPAN::VERSION >= 1.88_55) just:

   cpan .

